Title: Automating Report Generation to Simplify Workflows

Description:

Generating reports from existing dashboards can often require duplicating efforts, writing additional scripts, or relying on specific team members for implementation. This creates inefficiencies, dependencies, and maintenance overhead.

By leveraging automation tools like Selenium, we can simplify this process. A lightweight script combined with a configuration file can automate navigation, click actions, and report generation directly from the dashboard. This eliminates the need for extensive coding, reduces maintenance requirements, and minimizes dependency on specific individuals.

This approach not only saves time but also ensures consistency, scalability, and a seamless workflow for users, making the reporting process more efficient and independent.

